The elsarticle package contains the Elsevier article class for LaTeX.
It also includes some common manuscript templates, associated
bibliographic/BibTeX styles, and the relevant documentation. The
package is available on CTAN. The Elsevier article class ensures
proper formatting of manuscript for submission to jounals published
by Elsevier. elsarticle is based on the standard LaTeX document class
article.cls and uses natbib.sty for bibliographical references.

The elsarticle-texcls package wraps up the elsarticle CTAN package for
Slackware so that the class can be integrated safely into Slacware's
TeXlive environment safely.
